<plot>Since the death of his politically active father, Karim, 8, has not felt safe in his hometown of Karachi, Pakistan. Karim's overactive imagination is constantly getting the best of him and disrupting the lives of his siblings. In an attempt to convince Karim he has the courage to face the city, his older brother, Zahid, devises an adventure that will force Karim into the streets of Karachi. But will Karachi get the best of him?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?287069</url></doc>
